{"name": "script-launcher-ui", "metadata": {"name": "script-launcher-ui", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["PyQt6"], "summary": "A simple script launcher UI for configuration selection", "upload_time": 1735321905}, "documentation": ["# Script Launcher UI\n\nA simple PyQt6 based UI for script configuration and launching.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install script-launcher-ui\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nfrom script_launcher_ui import ScriptLauncherUI\n\ndef on_submit():\n    print(\"Configuration submitted\")\n\nui = ScriptLauncherUI(style='light')\nui.add_label('Welcome to Script Launcher')\nui.add_text_input_module('script_path', 'Script Path', 'Enter script path')\nui.add_button(\"Submit\", on_submit)\nui.start()\n```\n\n## Features\n\n- Simple and intuitive UI\n- Customizable styles\n- Configuration saving and loading\n- Easy integration with existing scripts\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"], "modules": [{"name": "script_launcher_ui", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "script_launcher_ui.ScriptLauncherUI", "xref": {"fqname": "script_launcher_ui.ui_library.ScriptLauncherUI", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "script_launcher_ui.ui_library", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "script_launcher_ui.ui_library.on_submit", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "script_launcher_ui.ui_library.ui", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "script_launcher_ui.ui_library.ScriptLauncherUI", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "script_launcher_ui.ui_library.ScriptLauncherUI.__init__", "a